#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:9
msgid "KGoldrunner"
msgstr "KGoldrunner"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Hunt Gold, Dodge Enemies and Solve Puzzles"
msgstr "Meklē zeltu, izvairies no pretiniekiem un risini mīklas"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KGoldrunner is an action game where the hero runs through a maze, climbs "
"stairs, dig holes and dodges enemies in order to collect all the gold "
"nuggets and escape to the next level. Your enemies are also after the gold. "
"Worse still, they are after you!."
msgstr ""
"„KGoldrunner“ ir darbības spēle, kurā tev, lai savāktu zelta gabalus un "
"tiktu nākamajā līmenī, ir jāatrod pareizas ceļš cauri labirintam, jākāpj pa "
"kāpnēm, jārok bedres un jāizvairās no pretiniekiem. Arī pretinieki vāc "
"zeltu, bet tas nav sliktākais — viņi cenšas tevi notvert!"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:17
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Iespējas:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:19
msgid "Themeable"
msgstr "Dažādi motīvi"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:20
msgid "Hundreds of levels"
msgstr "Simtiem līmeņu"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:21
msgid "Level-editor"
msgstr "Līmeņu redaktors"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:22
msgid ""
"Two modes for the enemies: classical and KGoldrunner-mode, in KGoldrunner-"
"mode they are more intelligent, in the classical mode it is easier to fool "
"them"
msgstr ""
"Divi pretinieku režīmi: klasiskais un „KGoldrunner“. „KGoldrunner“ režīmā "
"pretinieki ir gudrāki, bet klasiskajā režīmā viņus ir vieglāk apmuļķot"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:24
msgid "Very very difficult levels"
msgstr "Ārkārtīgi sarežģīti līmeņi"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:25
msgid "Keyboard or mouse control"
msgstr "Vadība ar tastatūru vai peli"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:26
msgid "Savable games"
msgstr "Spēli iespējams saglabāt"

